              "text": "## Canonical User Intent (already disambiguated by LLM)\r\nPause the execution of the current process for a short duration of 100 milliseconds\n## functions available starts ##\r\n{\"Description\":\"Wait, Sleep and time delay. Cron scheduler\",\"Methods\":[{\"Description\":\"WaitForExecution is always true when calling Sleep\",\"MethodName\":\"Sleep\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"sleepTimeInMilliseconds\",\"IsRequired\":true}]},{\"Description\":\"Waits increasingly in a key\",\"MethodName\":\"WaitIncreasingly\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"key\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.Int32]\",\"Name\":\"millisecondsDelay\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"timeoutInSeconds\",\"DefaultValue\":300,\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"MethodName\":\"WaitOnVariable\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"variableName\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int64\",\"Name\":\"timeInMilliseconds\",\"DefaultValue\":1000,\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"Description\":\"Use numerical representation for cronCommand, e.g. 0 11 * * 1. goalName is the goal that should be called, it should be prefixed by ! and be whole word with possible slash(/).\",\"MethodName\":\"Schedule\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"cronCommand\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalName\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.DateTime]\",\"Name\":\"nextRun\",\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"MethodName\":\"StartScheduler\",\"Parameters\":[]}],\"SupportingObjects\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Name\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2[System.String,System.Object]\",\"Name\":\"Parameters\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"WaitForExecution\",\"Description\":\"Whether to wait for the goal to complete before continuing. Default is true.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int64\",\"Name\":\"DelayWhenNotWaitingInMilliseconds\",\"Description\":\"Delay in milliseconds when not waiting for execution. Default is 50.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.UInt32\",\"Name\":\"WaitForXMillisecondsBeforeRunningGoal\",\"Description\":\"Wait for X milliseconds before running the goal. Default is 0.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"Isolated\",\"Description\":\"Run the goal in an isolated container. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"DisableSystemGoals\",\"Description\":\"Disable system/OS goals when running. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true}],\"IsRequired\":false}]}\r\n## functions available ends ##"
